results.name: Row sums of the Lambda triangle A160487
comment: In order to determine the row sums add the Maple line given below to the Lambda triangle algorithm, see A160487.
maple: for n from 2 to nmax do s(n):=0: for m from 1 to n-1 do s(n):=s(n) + LAMBDA(n,m) od: od: seq(s(n), n=2..nmax);
results.author: _Johannes W. Meijer_, May 24 2009
